          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>Same Day Appliance Repair serves:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Los Angeles</strong> <a href="/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">(see LA Service Hub)</a></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Orange County</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Ventura County</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-11">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Call Now for Sub-Zero Freezer Repair in Los Angeles</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>From Beverly Hills and West Hollywood to Pasadena and Irvine, we provide fast, high-end Sub-Zero freezer repair when you need it most. Book online at <a href="/services/refrigerator-repair-los-angeles/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">samedayappliance.repair</a> or call <strong>(323) 870-4790</strong> to schedule today.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-12">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>Same Day Appliance Repair is Southern California's trusted luxury appliance service provider. <strong>A+ BBB rated and factory-trained</strong>, we specialize in Sub-Zero and other premium brands. Our repairs are backed by a 90-day warranty and performed using official OEM parts. We serve <strong>Los Angeles, Glendale, Burbank, Santa Monica, Long Beach, Newport Beach, Thousand Oaks</strong>, and nearby cities with fast, professional service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <Contactbtn />
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
